i), (d)-(iii)","option_c_hi":"(a)-(ii), (b)-(i), (c)-(iv), (d)-(iii)","option_d_hi":"(a)-(iii), (b)-(i), (c)-(iv), (d)-(ii)"},{"id":842,"quiz_id":62,"topic_id":1013,"sort_order":22,"question":"Sri Krishnadevaraya, considered the greatest emperor of the Vijayanagara Empire, belonged to which of the following dynasties?","question_hi":"विजयनगर साम्राज्य के सबसे महान सम्राट माने जाने वाले श्री कृष्णदेवराय, निम्नलिखित में से किस राजवंश से संबंधित थे?","option_a":"Sangama","option_b":"Saluva","option_c":"Tuluva","option_d":"Aravidu","option_a_hi":"संगम","option_b_hi":"सालुव","option_c_hi":"तुलुव","option_d_hi":"अराविडु"},{"id":843,"quiz_id":62,"topic_id":1013,"sort_order":23,"question":"Consider the following statements regarding the social conditions in the Vijayanagara Empire as described by foreign travelers:\\n\\n1. Women held prominent positions; Fernao Nuniz noted that they were employed as accountants, wrestlers, and astrologers.\\n\\n2. The practice of Sati (Sahagamana) was prevalent and was recorded in detail by travelers like Nuniz and Barbosa.\\n\\nChoose the correct answer:","question_hi":"विदेशी यात्रियों द्वारा वर्णित विजयनगर साम्राज्य में सामाजिक स्थितियों के संदर्भ में निम्नलिखित कथनों पर विचार कीजिए:\\n\\n1. महिलाओं के पास प्रमुख पद थे; फर्नाओ नूनीज़ ने उल्लेख किया कि उन्हें एकाउंटेंट, पहलवान और ज्योतिषी के रूप में नियुक्त किया गया था।\\n\\n2. सती प्रथा (सहगमन) प्रचलित थी और नूनीज़ और बारबोसा जैसे यात्रियों द्वारा इसका विस्तार से वर्णन किया गया था।\\n\\nसही विकल्प चुनें:","option_a":"Only 1","option_b":"Only 2","option_c":"Both 1 and 2","option_d":"Neither 1 nor 2","option_a_hi":"केवल 1","option_b_hi":"केवल 2","option_c_hi":"1 और 2 दोनों","option_d_hi":"न तो 1 और न ही 2"},{"id":844,"quiz_id":62,"topic_id":1013,"sort_order":24,"question":"Arrange the rulers of the Tuluva dynasty in their correct chronological sequence:\\n\\n1. Achyuta Deva Raya\\n2. Krishnadevaraya\\n3. Vira Narasimha Raya\\n4. Sadasiva Raya\\n\\nChoose the correct code:","question_hi":"त